text: Johan Isaac Westergren (12 July 1875 – 16 October 1950) was a Swedish sprinter. He competed at the 1900 Summer Olympics in the 60 m and 100 m events, but failed to reach the finals. ==References== ==Further reading== * De Wael, Herman. Herman's Full Olympians: "Athletics 1900".
